	   <tr><td colspan=2>Do your pets really take exp? And if so, how much? I'm starting to play EQ now, and I was thinking of starting with a mage, but I have to know how much exp do the pets take, and if it's worth it to play a mage, even with that downside? Thanks in advance, and sorry for my bad english :)<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
