	   <tr><td colspan=2>The reason people are so divided on the question of which race is best for mage is simple : we are the least mana dependant casters in the game. Our pets do most of the work...<br><br>What this means is that ANY of the allowable classes make good mages. Having a large mana pool is nice but 99% of the time you don't use it all.<br><br>The real answer as to what racce is best for mages is simple : what race appeals to you the most - they all work well.<br>&nbsp;<br>Zyphyr Runnersbane<br>60th Vending Machine<br>Cult of the Ancient Wyrm<br>Solusek Ro<br></td></tr>
